<h3>
	Vision Health and Fitness Club | Getting ready for GDPR
</h3>

<p>Please confirm that you are still happy to hear from us.</p>

<p>Dear <%= "#{@member.first_name} #{@member.last_name}" %></p>

<% if @member.member_type == 'member' && @member.active? %>

	<p>
	You may have already heard that a new law is coming into effect on the 25thMay this year called The EU General Data Protection Regulation or GDPR. It is possibly the most important change in data privacy regulation in 20 years. At Vision we are committed to protecting the privacy of personal data of all members, past, present and future. In preparation for when the  GDPR will be enforced, we would like to verify that you are happy to continue receiving  marketing material from us via email and or text.
	</p>

	<p>
	By giving your consent you will continue to receive relevant gym promotions, special offers or other related subjects that we  feel would be of interest to you. You may also wish to read our updated Privacy Policyi that provides full details about how we use your personal data. 
	</p>

	<p>
	If you decide that you do not want to receive marketing content from us any longer, please be aware that we may still have to contact you regarding your existing membership, servicing information, class timetable amendments or other matters directly relating to your  membership and or use of the gym.
	</p>

	<p>
	If you are happy to receive promotions and special offers from us going forward then please click the 'Opt-in' link below. If you no longer wish to receive them, simply ignore this email and do not click on the opt in link. You have the right to withdraw your consent at any time and can unsubscribe just as easily by clicking the provided link in any future emails. If we have not heard from you by May 25th then we will not send you any further marketing information unless you request it by clicking the opt in link.
	</p>

	<p>
	We thank you for your valued membership, continued support and look forward to seeing you in the gym soon. Best wishes,Vision Health and Fitness Club Limited
	</p>

<p>
	<%= "https://visionhealthandfitness.co.uk/members/#{@member.consent_to_market_token}" %>
</p>

<% else %>

